{"tid":1561152,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民狙擊CCTVB偽人活動]9月13號晚上7點半沙田公園","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T23:32:36.000Z","uid":17646,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"31ee2b96400e807f3915962572915721ec0c40bc","tid":1561152,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">為何要狙擊CCTVB偽人活動</span></span><br />\n新聞部屢次刪改事實之全部,偏僻藍絲<br />\n我地要全面打擊CCTVB收入來源,偽人(所謂親生仔女)每一次出席任何活動/拍攝廣,CCTVB會抽佣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">如何狙擊</span></span><br />\n只需大家係偽人出場時,採訪時大嗌口號影響活動進行,PR會考慮即時腰斬(馬明事件),而CCTVB收入同時會大幅減少<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日期： 13/9/2019<br />\n活動： 月滿歡樂聚沙田中秋晚會2019<br />\n嘉賓： 安德尊、梁嘉琪、胡鴻鈞、菊梓喬、<br />\n          陳潔靈、何雁詩、林師傑、謝㺭圻、<br />\n          周志康、楊潮凱、伍富橋、林凱恩、<br />\n          李行齊。<br />\n時間： 19:30 - 22:30<br />\n地點： 沙田公園及沙田大會堂廣場</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只需一百人以上參與就可以成事</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">13號當晚大家唔好帶同雞蛋到場</span></span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=5265872d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: sayno2tvb<br />\nTVB廣告客戶名單 (消費前諗清楚): <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=6bdf3494\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a><br />\n已加入myTV SUPER廣告、產品代言清單<br />\n<br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=5c7eb71f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊活動行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/tvbfucker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbfucker&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=77a44b0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tvbfucker</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/shittytvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshittytvb&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=5ced51fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/shittytvb</a>"},{"pid":"9e750bfd75cc335524b3ed464f058f93e23e1212","tid":1561152,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9ecfea0d7a7e40539b64f4178c65d5c10afb842c","tid":1561152,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"推！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請即參與：#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1560141/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1560141/page/1</a><br />\n已有手足推緊hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n向外國人宣傳警暴！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=18ff7fd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n<strong>或者share以下既圖去twitter加一兩張黑警圖！</strong><br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n3. 叫埋外國人一齊Report俾WhatsApp聽，增加noise<br />\n尾數雙數先係business，單數係正常account<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係兩種acc都違反晒terms of service！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n班狗想分散投資，不過我地要port到佢一條不留！<br />\n<br />\n祝大家舉報愉快<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yxr6aC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yxr6aC.jpg&h=ab2b926e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqeBKbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqeBKbL.jpg&h=93c8393e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"010eb8deade0e18a727fd1d95d0bfcccb3f9ec62","tid":1561152,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e3ec4951bcad2e7ed2a1ffde97a2b566a546631","tid":1561152,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:42:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只需一百人以上參與就可以成事</span></span><br />\nTG 狙擊活動行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/tvbfucker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbfucker&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=77a44